Package: EcoCalendar
Type: Package
Title: Create daily calendars of economic releases
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ulrich", "Leuchtmann", 
                  email = "ulrich.leuchtmann@t-online.de", 
                  role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Dependent on the list provided in "ecoitems.csv", the functions 
             create a list of economic data releases, pupulate them with 
             information from Bloomberg and create png files with formatted
             tables.
